ANNOUNCEMENT
Please be informed of the schedule of Colleges who will report onsite for the limited face-to-face classes at the Pamantasan ng Lungsod ng Muntinlupa, for the month of October 2022. Only those students with classes (based on GCR) under the scheduled College per day are asked to report onsite. Kindly visit the Official Facebook page of the Pamantasan ng Lungsod ng Muntinlupa.
